'''印度[[瑪撒拉|瑪撒拉]]香料捲餅'''是独特的[[印度南部|南印度]]薄餅料理，它最早是源自於[[图鲁纳德|圖魯納德]]地區的傳統[[门格洛尔|門格洛爾]]（又譯：芒加羅）料理，後由於[[烏杜皮|烏杜皮]]市的旅館業有提供此道料理而受歡迎，最後甚至普及整個印度。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://food.ndtv.com/how-to/india-crisped-on-a-griddle-classic-masala-dosa-734820|title=India, Crisped on a Griddle: Classic Masala dosa|publisher=NDTV food|website=Food.ndtv.com|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811135751/https://food.ndtv.com/how-to/india-crisped-on-a-griddle-classic-masala-dosa-734820|dead-url=no}}</ref> 瑪撒拉捲餅使用的材料有：蒸穀米、印度黑豆仁或[[扁豆|扁豆]]、[[胡芦巴|葫蘆巴]]籽、印度扁米片、[[咖哩葉|咖哩葉]]、馬鈴薯，並且搭配著傳統印度[[酸辣醬|酸辣醬]]以及[[酸豆|酸]][[扁豆|扁豆]]燉菜湯食用。儘管瑪撒拉捲餅料理在南印度比較普及，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/masala-dosa-slips-out-of-reach/article6110691.ece|title=Masala dosa slips out of reach|date=13 June 2014|publisher=The Hindu|last2=Krishnakumar|first2=G.|location=Chennai, India|first1=M. P.|last1=Praveen|accessdate=2017-03-18|archive-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618072450/http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/masala-dosa-slips-out-of-reach/article6110691.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但在印度全國各地，甚至海外也都吃得到。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.in/2015/03/16/masala-dosa-sarvana-bhava_n_6875582.html|title=What A Masala dosa Costs Around The World|publisher=Huffingtonpost India|website=Huffingtonpost.in|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809031513/https://www.huffingtonpost.in/2015/03/16/masala-dosa-sarvana-bhava_n_6875582.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/11/magazine/masala-dosa-to-die-for.html?_r=0|title=Masala dosa to Die For|last=Romig|first=Rollo|date=7 May 2014|publisher=The New York Times|website=Nytimes.com/|accessdate=2017-03-18|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012248/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/11/magazine/masala-dosa-to-die-for.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sfchronicle.com/entertainment/article/Dosa-s-complex-spices-hit-the-spot-6158614.php|title=Dosa’s complex spices hit the spot|publisher=San Francisco chronicle|website=Sfchronicle.com/|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217162046/https://www.sfchronicle.com/entertainment/article/Dosa-s-complex-spices-hit-the-spot-6158614.php|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這道菜在南印度不同城市會有不同的料理方式。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/2010/12/16/forbes-india-hunt-for-perfect-dosa-in-nyc.html|title=American Dosa|last=Ramnath|first=N.S.|publisher=Forbes|website=Forbes.com/|accessdate=2017-03-18|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805122021/https://www.forbes.com/2010/12/16/forbes-india-hunt-for-perfect-dosa-in-nyc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 料理方式 ==
瑪撒拉香料捲餅簡單說，就是有包內餡的煎薄餅。所以料理上，可以分成兩個步驟，一個製作煎餅，一個製作內餡。煎餅部分跟其他印度傳統薄餅製作方式一樣，將米、黑豆仁或扁豆泡水一晚，然後連同葫蘆巴籽、印度扁米片放入一個容器裡一起攪拌搗碎製作成麵糊，這樣就可以開始做煎餅了。餡料則是將水煮過的馬鈴薯和芥末籽等所有香料一起下去煮做成馬鈴薯[[咖哩|咖哩]]，再添加[[椰子|椰子]]粉、[[香菜|香菜]]和[[檸檬汁|檸檬汁]]點綴。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jX1D-meFyvYC&pg=PA43&dq=masala+dosa&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiExPqoh67LAhWDJI4KHWEzDZwQ6AEIGzAA#v=onepage&q=masala%20dosa&f=false|title=Modern Cookery Book|date=1993|publisher=Pustak Mahal|isbn=978-81-223-0470-1|last1=Vohra|first1=Asha Rani}}</ref>

[[邁索爾|邁索爾]]瑪撒拉香料捲餅則是將紅[[辣椒|辣椒]]、[[洋蔥|洋蔥]]和[[蒜頭|蒜頭]]做成的紅[[酸辣醬|酸辣醬]]直接加到薄煎餅裡，然後才把馬鈴薯內餡放上去捲起來。

