一般常見的食材包含：蒸穀米、印度黑豆仁、芥末籽、[[胡芦巴|葫蘆巴]]籽、[[食盐|鹽]]、蔬菜油、馬鈴薯、洋蔥、印度綠辣椒、[[咖哩葉|咖哩葉]]、以及[[薑黃|薑黃]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://food.ndtv.com/recipe-masala-dosa-219232|title=Masala dosa|publisher=NDTV food|website=Food.ndtv.com/|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223050831/https://food.ndtv.com/recipe-masala-dosa-219232|dead-url=no}}</ref>

